'''威廉·魏特林'''（{{Bd|1808年|10月5日|1871年|1月24日}}）<ref name="query.nytimes.com">{{Cite web |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9406EFD9133EEE34BC4F51DFB766838A669FDE |title=Obituary in New York Times, January 27, 1871, Wednesday |access-date=2011-08-22 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103646/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9406EFD9133EEE34BC4F51DFB766838A669FDE |dead-url=no }}</ref>是[[普魯士|普魯士]]裁缝、发明家、19世纪[[欧洲|欧洲]]重要的[[激进主义|激进主义者]]。威廉·魏特林曾被[[马克思|马克思]]和[[恩格斯|恩格斯]]评价为[[空想社会主义|空想社会主义者]]，<ref>Isaiah Berlin, ''Karl Marx: His Life and Environment'', 4th ed. (Oxford University Press US, 1996: ISBN 0195103262), p. 81.</ref><ref>Tristram Hunt, ''Marx's General: The Revolutionary Life of Friedrich Engels'' (Henry Holt and Co., 2009: ISBN 0805080252), p. 132.</ref>同时恩格斯也认为他是“[[德国|德国]][[共产主义|共产主义]]的创始人”。<ref>[http://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1843/10/23.htm Frederick Engels: Progress of Social Reform On the Continent, II Germany and Switzerland] {{Wayback|url=http://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1843/10/23.htm |date=20210816145812 }}, ''The New Moral World'' No. 21, November 18, 1843</ref>1842年魏特林發表《和諧與自由的保證》（Garantien der Harmonie und Freiheit）<ref>{{cite news |title=《世界历史大事编年精要》 |url=http://read.nongyekx.cn/gopreview?title=1844%E5%B9%B4%E8%A5%BF%E9%87%8C%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%E7%BA%BA%E7%BB%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B7%E4%B9%89&ssid=12078975&dxid=000006620927& |publisher=王春良，刘文涛主编 北京：星球地图出版社 2008 第155页}}</ref>。1871年魏特林在[[美國|美國]][[紐約|紐約]]去世<ref name=times>[https://archive.org/details/710127NytWeitlingobit "Wilhelm Weitling: An Inventor of Prominence — A Remarkable Career,"] ''New York Times,'' Jan. 27, 1871.</ref>。

